1. Write a program to create String array and print all the values in that array.
  public class arrayassignment {
public static void main(String[] args) {
		String days []= {"monday","tuesday","wednesday","thursday","friday"};
		for (int i=0;i<days.length;i++) {
			System.out.println(days[i]);
		}
		}
}

2. Write a sample program for while loop and do-while loop.
  sample program :Print odd numbers from 1 to 20.using while loop & do while loop.
       WHILE LOOP:
  int a=1;
	while(a<=20) {
		if(a%2!=0) {
			System.out.println("odd number from 1to 20:" +a);
			
		}a++;
	}
		
	DO WHILE LOOP:
	int b=1;
	do {
		if(b%2!=0) {
			System.out.println("odd number from  1to 20:" +b);
		}b++;
	}while(b<=20);
